title: 47 in. D-Handle Digging Shovel
description: This all-steel shovel features a D-handle design for comfortable, two-handed control on all of your heavy-duty digging tasks. A sharpened blade cuts into hard ground with ease, and an oversized step provides a comfortable platform for your foot to provide even more power. The welded steel construction makes this shovel virtually unbreakable, and a powder coat prevents rust and makes it easy to keep your shovel clean. Lifetime warranty.
